panels.title: Credits Details based on Membership Status

targets.rawSql:
SELECT memberships.name as Membership, uprofiles.first_name as Profile, users.name as User_Name, uprofiles.email as Email, memberships.status as Status, memberships.price as Original_Price, purchases.subtotal as Final_Price, memberships.created_at as Creation_Date, umemberships.expiration_date as Expiration_Date
FROM
    dev.memberships as memberships
JOIN
    dev.users_memberships as umemberships ON memberships.id = umemberships.memberships_id
JOIN
    dev.user_profiles as uprofiles ON umemberships.user_profiles_id = uprofiles.id
JOIN
    dev.users as users ON users.id = uprofiles.users_id
JOIN
    dev.purchases as purchases ON purchases.users_id = users.id
WHERE
    memberships.created_at BETWEEN CONVERT_TZ(FROM_UNIXTIME($__unixEpochFrom()), '+00:00', '-05:00')
                      AND CONVERT_TZ(FROM_UNIXTIME($__unixEpochTo()), '+00:00', '-05:00')

SELECT memberships.name as Membership, uprofiles.first_name as Profile, users.name as User_Name, uprofiles.email as Email, locations.name as Location, memberships.status as Status, memberships.price as Original_Price, pitems.item_price_final as Item_Price, pitems.item_credits as Item_Credits, credits.name as Credit_Name, purchases.subtotal as Final_Price, memberships.created_at as Creation_Date, umemberships.expiration_date as Expiration_Date
FROM
    dev.memberships as memberships
JOIN
    dev.users_memberships as umemberships ON memberships.id = umemberships.memberships_id
JOIN
    dev.user_profiles as uprofiles ON umemberships.user_profiles_id = uprofiles.id
JOIN
    dev.users as users ON users.id = uprofiles.users_id
JOIN
    dev.membership_credits as mcredits ON mcredits.memberships_id = memberships.id
JOIN
    dev.credits as credits ON credits.id = mcredits.credits_id
JOIN
    dev.purchase_items as pitems ON pitems.users_id = users.id
JOIN
    dev.purchases as purchases ON purchases.id = pitems.purchases_id
JOIN
    dev.locations as locations ON locations.id = pitems.locations_id

WHERE
    memberships.created_at BETWEEN CONVERT_TZ(FROM_UNIXTIME($__unixEpochFrom()), '+00:00', '-05:00')
                      AND CONVERT_TZ(FROM_UNIXTIME($__unixEpochTo()), '+00:00', '-05:00')
